Class CarNoneLearning

    sajas.core.TimerListener

    public class CarNoneLearning
extends Car
    It's an extended class of car just with the purpose of handling the debug messages in a different way and to enable the choice of a different icon in the repast display, such that it can be easily distinguished in the space from the other cars. The color of this car is red.
